₹2000 ki padi ye saari pics !! kyunki jahan gaye the, woh ek restricted area tha kabhi bhi paani ka flow badh sakta tha aur pura flood ho sakta tha. But bro, jab location itni aesthetic ho to I don’t give a damn . 

We climbed down a trippy hillside trail, no actual route, just full adventure mode ON. It was near sunset, vibes were heavy, shots were insane. But then... ek police vale ne humari photos kheenchni start kar di . 

Eventually, I paid the fine but tbh, I call it my ‘aesthetic accessibility fee’. 2–2.5 hours of pure peace, beauty and madness. Fine diya par fun nahi chhoda aur waise bhi, yaadein priceless hoti hain .
